{"tid":262340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齊昕po暴瘦出浴照 自爆「那時還覺得自己很肥」","createTime":"2017-05-29T07:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T09:29:40.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"309d6c3bb97af7fc27e3a5710841aa82e3f5fc0d","tid":262340,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496041097_4f9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496041097_4f9e.png&h=f1f005e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近甚少公開露面的特首梁振英次女梁齊昕，近日在Instagram上載與愛犬的合照。戴上黑超的齊昕，以雙手勉強抱起愛犬，狀甚吃力，留言慨嘆「Can't carry my heavy baby anymore!」。<br />\n<br />\n齊昕又回顧昔日的「暴瘦」模貌，上載一張翻拍螢幕的性感出浴照，但未有標明何時拍攝。相中的齊昕以手巾和手機遮蓋敏感部位，露出玉背和手臂，但瘦至鎖骨附近凹陷，嚴重寒背。回看舊照，齊昕也自覺當時「太瘦了，記得那時還覺得自己很肥」。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月，梁齊昕向雜誌透露，之前因貪靚而努力減肥，試過瘦至84磅，自言「沖涼嗰陣都嚇親」，「得棚骨咁樣」，如今按醫生指示服用抗抑鬱藥，並已服用3個月，亦知道服藥會令身形發脹及水腫，但為健康着想，一直乖乖服藥，又謂「睇得好開」，最重要是肥得健康又開心。"},{"pid":"f8b546b0df5eb65cebedb3b17114b37a6ac9ee2d","tid":262340,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"講還講..."},{"pid":"dde86ee0aa3c033f86047e187ac14a6f29f329da","tid":262340,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fac9b06fa4f382e557ff39b3dd9a478775d7c35","tid":262340,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個馬蹄露咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47dae98317a9a80bc15cc2151e5df65809518666","tid":262340,"uid":385